      <h1>Careers at Storitz</h1>

      <p>
        We're searching for some great technical folks to join the Storitz team.  Storitz uses state of the art technology to
        build out the site and need people who eat, breathe and sleep Groovy/Grails, jQuery, CSS, MySQL and Linux. We leverage
        technology to highly automate our industry and need sharp technical people want to apply technology to solve a lot of
        tough problems.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are located in West Los Angeles right off the 405 Freeway.  Our offices are a short walk to 20 or 30 restaurants. We have
        a great group of people and would love energized, talented folks to email a resume and cover letter to <a href="mailto:jobs@storitz.com">jobs@storitz.com</a>
      </p>
